summary: AN ORDINANCE relating to license fees for peepshows; reducing and eliminating certain fees for peepshows and subjecting those businesses to amusement device license fees effective January 1, 1990; and amending Seattle Municipal Code (SMC) Sections 5.32.140, 5.32.160, 6.42.010, 6.42.020, 6.42.030, 6.42.040, and 6.42.060.
